notes:
As of May 2, North Dakota is reporting people tested. On 5/3, ND began providing counts of deaths for lab-confirmed individuals with death records still pending, and lab-confirmed individuals who died but not due to COVID. As of 7/1, we have edited our figures to exclude these numbers from our death counts, resulting in an apparent drop from 24 deaths on 5/2 to 16 on 5/3. On 6/18, ND revised down its confirmed death count from 66 to 64. On 
6/24, ND revised its confirmed death count from 67 to 66 to remove an 
out-of-state case.
name: North Dakota
